textBeforeTable: English—Worldwide TCG sets This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. This card can only be Special Summoned to your opponent's side of the field by Tributing 2 monsters your opponent controls. You cannot Normal Summon or Set during the turn this monster is Special Summoned. This card's controller takes 700 damage during each of their End Phases.
